  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<blockquote><p>Prerequisite: Level 5+ Warlock</p></blockquote><p>As a Magic action, you alter time around a creature of your choice you can see within 60 feet. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw or be affected by this invocation for one minute.</p><p>An affected target's Speed is halved, it takes a -2 penalty to AC and Dexterity saving throws, and it can't take Reactions. On its turn, it can use either an action or a Bonus Action, not both, and it can make only one attack if it takes the Attack action. If it casts a spell with a Somatic component, there is a 25 percent chance the spell fails as a result of the target making the spell's gestures too slowly.</p><p>An affected target repeats the same save at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success.</p>",
